{"tid":852589,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟促港府澄清拒向馬凱續發工作簽證原因","createTime":"2018-10-08T03:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T05:24:10.000Z","uid":41404,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"94165112672bd2e62e64ed8b3ea2fd884f2396ec","tid":852589,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:09:00.000Z","msg":"任職《金融時報》的外國記者會副主席馬凱被特區政府拒續發工作簽證，繼英國要求港府立即解釋、美國炮轟港府做法不符《基本法》後，今日連歐盟也發聲，質疑有關決定。<br />\n歐洲聯盟駐港澳辦事處發言人回覆查詢時指，歐盟正密切留意事件，並期望香港政府澄清拒絕向一名記者發出簽證的原因，歐盟又為香港表達和新聞自由本受《基本法》和《公民權利及政治權利國際公約》所保障，如今卻引起一個正式疑問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181008/58769179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58769179&d=iI5Tuu4jwIiV0%2BmkkSMa5e9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=4fb1be9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58769179&h=14af2925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181008/58769179</a>"},{"pid":"0dc7357252409073536c4e9c027cb9b40fb945c7","tid":852589,"uid":206080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:09:46.000Z","msg":"連歐盟都出聲"},{"pid":"2186d763912322fcc8872b83f8bcd76449135159","tid":852589,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"歐盟駐港澳辦事處回覆查詢全文：<br />\n<strong>The EU is following this issue closely and expects the HK government to clarify the reasons of the refusal to grant visa to a journalist. This incident raises legitimate questions about the freedom of press and expression in HK, which are guaranteed by HK&rsquo;s Basic Law and ICCPR.&quot;</strong>"},{"pid":"5d2d800db23d22e29d48e4a80c9c39b9f0cd9bd9","tid":852589,"uid":17103,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:12:36.000Z","msg":"&quot; 我鍾意, 吹呀? &quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/ha